---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 6, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use"
  description="Read the Terms of Use for Integrity Real Estate Corp's website. Understand your rights and responsibilities when using our Philippine real estate portal."
>
  <Navbar />

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">

    <div class="mb-10">
      <p class="text-[#ea580c] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-8">

      <div class="bg-orange-50 border border-orange-100 rounded-xl p-5 text-sm text-orange-800">
        Please read these Terms of Use carefully before using the website operated by <strong>Integrity Real Estate Corp</strong>. By accessing or using <strong>integrityrealty.ph</strong>, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use our website.
      </div>

      <!-- 1. Acceptance -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">These Terms of Use (&quot;Terms&quot;) constitute a legally binding agreement between you (&quot;User&quot;) and <strong>Integrity Real Estate Corp</strong> (&quot;Company&quot;, &quot;we&quot;, &quot;our&quot;). By using this website, you confirm that you are at least 18 years of age and capable of entering into a binding agreement under Philippine law.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 2. Description of Service -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">Integrity Real Estate Corp provides an online real estate portal that allows users to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Browse residential, commercial, and land property listings in the Philippines</li>
          <li>Submit inquiries to licensed real estate agents</li>
          <li>Save and compare property listings</li>
          <li>Access guides and resources related to real estate transactions</li>
          <li>List properties for sale or rent (subject to approval)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any feature of our website at any time without prior notice.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 3. Property Listings -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">3. Property Listings and Accuracy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">All property listings on this website are provided for informational purposes only. While we strive for accuracy, we make no warranties regarding:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1 mb-3">
          <li>The accuracy, completeness, or current availability of any listing</li>
          <li>The actual condition, title status, or legal encumbrances of any property</li>
          <li>Prices, which are subject to change without notice</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You are solely responsible for independently verifying all property information before making any real estate decision. We strongly recommend engaging a licensed broker, attorney, and conducting due diligence including title verification with the Registry of Deeds.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 4. User Accounts -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">4. User Accounts</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">If you create an account on our website, you agree to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Provide accurate, complete, and current registration information</li>
          <li>Maintain the confidentiality of your login credentials</li>
          <li>Immediately notify us of any unauthorized use of your account</li>
          <li>Accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms or engage in fraudulent or harmful activity.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 5. Prohibited Uses -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">5. Prohibited Uses</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">You agree not to use this website to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Post false, misleading, or fraudulent property listings</li>
          <li>Harvest or scrape contact information or listings for mass solicitation</li>
          <li>Impersonate any person or entity, including our agents or staff</li>
          <li>Upload or transmit malicious code, viruses, or harmful content</li>
          <li>Violate any applicable Philippine law, including the Cybercrime Prevention Act (RA 10175)</li>
          <li>Use automated bots or scrapers without our written permission</li>
          <li>Interfere with or disrupt the operation of our website or servers</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- 6. Intellectual Property -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">All content on this website — including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, icons, images, and software — is the property of Integrity Real Estate Corp or its content suppliers and is protected by Philippine and international copyright laws.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">You may not reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works from any content on this website without our prior written consent. Limited personal, non-commercial use is permitted provided you do not remove any copyright notices.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 7. Third-Party Services -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">7. Third-Party Links and Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Our website may contain links to third-party websites or integrate third-party services (including mapping services, payment processors, and social media platforms). These links are provided for convenience only. We do not endorse, control, or assume responsibility for the content, privacy practices, or terms of any third-party website or service.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 8. Disclaimers -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">8. Disclaimers and Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">This website and all content are provided on an &quot;as is&quot; and &quot;as available&quot; basis without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">To the maximum extent permitted by Philippine law, Integrity Real Estate Corp shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising from:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-1">
          <li>Your use of or inability to use our website</li>
          <li>Any real estate transaction or decision made based on information from our website</li>
          <li>Unauthorized access to or alteration of your data</li>
          <li>Any content posted or transmitted by third parties on our website</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3">Our total liability for any claim arising from these Terms shall not exceed the amount you paid us (if any) in the 12 months preceding the claim.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 9. Real Estate Disclosures -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">9. Real Estate Regulatory Disclosures</h2>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5 text-gray-600 space-y-3">
          <p>Integrity Real Estate Corp is a licensed real estate brokerage operating in the Philippines under the <strong>Real Estate Service Act (RA 9646)</strong>.</p>
          <p>All property transactions facilitated through our platform involve licensed real estate brokers or salespersons accredited by the <strong>Professional Regulation Commission (PRC)</strong>.</p>
          <p>Lease agreements are subject to the <strong>Rent Control Act (RA 9653)</strong> where applicable. Buyers are advised to verify title status with the relevant <strong>Registry of Deeds</strong> and conduct due diligence before any purchase.</p>
          <p>Commission structures and brokerage fees are governed by the Schedule of Fees under RA 9646 and are disclosed separately in engagement letters.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- 10. Privacy -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">10. Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Your use of our website is also governed by our <a href="/privacy" class="text-[#ea580c] hover:underline font-medium">Privacy Policy</a>, which is incorporated into these Terms by reference. By using our website, you consent to the collection and use of your information as described in our Privacy Policy.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 11. Governing Law -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">11. Governing Law and Dispute Resolution</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the Republic of the Philippines. Any dispute arising out of or relating to these Terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of <strong>Metro Manila, Philippines</strong>.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Before initiating legal proceedings, both parties agree to attempt good-faith resolution through written notice and 30-day negotiation period.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- 12. Changes -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 pb-2 border-b border-gray-100">12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be effective upon posting to our website with an updated &quot;Last updated&quot; date. Continued use of the website after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms. We recommend reviewing these Terms periodically.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact -->
      <section class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Questions About These Terms?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 text-sm">If you have questions, concerns, or need clarification about these Terms of Use, please contact us:</p>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <p>📧 <a href="mailto:info@integrityrealty.ph" class="text-[#ea580c] hover:underline">info@integrityrealty.ph</a></p>
          <p>📍 Metro Manila, Philippines</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/contact" class="text-sm bg-[#ea580c] hover:bg-[#c2410c] text-white font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-colors">Contact Us</a>
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-sm border border-gray-200 hover:border-[#ea580c] text-gray-600 hover:text-[#ea580c] px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
